column2: "Ah, <%me>. Are you okay? You're not hurt, right?"
"It looks like you're fine. Just don't take Zeno's example, got that?"
"Well, to be honest, Zeno's really settled down compared to how he used to be."
"Speaking of, have you seen him? He seems to have run off somewhere."
"If you find him, be sure to tell him I'm looking for him."
"Zeno was looking for me too? He said that I ran off on my own?"
"I wasn't just running off. It seemed like there was something up ahead."
"Either way, it's his fault for being slow!"
"I'm going to get back to looking for him. Later!"
